issue.title: TypeUnion::getTypes has incorrect documented return type

Support implicitly determining ServiceDelegate based on method return type

milestone.title: v1.3 Release
milestone.description: Quality of life improvements and useful features when using Attributes.

issue.body: Currently the `#[ServiceDelegate]` Attribute requires that you provide the FCQN of the Service that should be created by the annotated method. If the method includes the return type for an object we could use that instead and only require the Service be passed to `#[ServiceDelegate]` in situations where the return type cannot be used to infer it.

issue.title: Release next version for conditional configuration checking
issue.body: It would be helpful if there was an official release for the conditional checking of the configuration ID being present. Right now this winds up resulting in the app not even loading if the value isn't present. The code is present just need a new version.

issue.title: Extension class not removed after query
issue.body: In the current version of the application the extension class is never removed after the query is executed.  Ultimately this means that if a user clicks on an already split vote count again they will needlessly execute another query to the SE API, eating into the API quota limit.
